description: A day at the beach with fun activities including calisthenics, games, and a bonfire to wrap it all up.
Second General Body Meeting where we discuss the progress of the club and upcoming events.
A casual evening to relax and socialize with other club members.
Join us at the beach as we induct new members into their workout families!
Travel with us to Santa Monica for a bar jam session with UCLA's calisthenics club.
Wear your best costume and join us for a spooky workout session followed by a costume contest.
Our annual calisthenics competition with categories for strength, speed, and skill. Join us for a beginner friendly competition to show off your progress and win prizes!
Final General Body Meeting of the quarter to wrap up and discuss future plans.
A day filled with team-based challenges and outdoor activities to build camaraderie.
Dress up and join us for a formal dinner to celebrate the end of the quarter.
